Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:56.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起死回生を図った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:56.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グー買い占め作戦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.73,default,,0,0,0,,The Rock-hoarding strategy was\Nsupposed to revive their chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.74,default,,0,0,0,,But it was utterly defeated\Nby Kitami's Paper-hoarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:01:00.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし北見の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:01:00.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パー買い占めにより破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.54,default,,0,0,0,,It will be a death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスマッチだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちかが完全に星を吐き出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:06.44,default,,0,0,0,,We play until either side\Nloses all his stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室に行くまでやる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろ 茶髪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine,\Nbrown-haired one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.48,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Deadly Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:17.18,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.29,default,,0,0,0,,- Kaiji...\N- Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.53,default,,0,0,0,,So, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするもこうするもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.26,default,,0,0,0,,Crazy fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:31.06,default,,0,0,0,,Neither way will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:34.03,default,,0,0,0,,I will quit after this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は１試合で切り上げるって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:38.02,default,,0,0,0,,There will be no such thing\Nas a death match!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスマッチもクソもねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話にもならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:42.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:42.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.57,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:41.78,default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったよ　２試合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２試合でどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:45.67,default,,0,0,0,,I get it! Two games then.\NHow about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,You're hounding me.\NGive me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くどいんだよ　いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,I said one match only!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１試合だけって言ってんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:56.52,default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった　分かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１試合でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.30,default,,0,0,0,,One match will do.\NPlease, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む １試合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:02.98,default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you should have said so\Nin the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初からそう言やいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.40,default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:14.00,default,,0,0,0,,The battle of Kaiji\Nagainst Kitami begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ対北見　開戦である
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？１試合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泣いても笑っても１試合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.97,default,,0,0,0,,Listen, just one game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.28,default,,0,0,0,,Whether you laugh or cry,\Nit's just one game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.92,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,構わないな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.25,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.72,default,,0,0,0,,Then let's begin, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ いくか カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いちにの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.10,default,,0,0,0,,Get in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.46,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.98,default,,0,0,0,,W-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:39.11,default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビビってんのか てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.02,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:50.96,default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, it's no use\Nholding on to all this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカネ 余らせても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょうがないと思ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ負けたら別室行き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.28,default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'll be going\Nto the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:59.75,default,,0,0,0,,In that case, how about betting\Nthree stars in this one game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:03:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら この勝負 １試合に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:03:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つをかけるってのはどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.29,default,,0,0,0,,No way! What rubbish\Nwere you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな 何めちゃくちゃ言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなルール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.42,default,,0,0,0,,- The rules!\N- There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ない　当事者が納得ずくなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:09.73,default,,0,0,0,,So long as the players agree,\Nthere isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的には問題ないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.03,default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.96,default,,0,0,0,,The proof is that this guy here\Nin a suit isn't stopping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この黒服が聞き流してるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい証拠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.99,default,,0,0,0,,Even so, one star is\Nworth five million now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:21.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:21.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 星は１つ500万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.16,default,,0,0,0,,Your six million isn't\Neven enough for two stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の600万じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星２つと釣り合わねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.34,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　早まるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.65,default,,0,0,0,,Wait! \NDon't jump to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,600万は星２つの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代わりじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.28,default,,0,0,0,,The six million is not\Nfor the two stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたら ただ黙って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらへ差し出すボーナスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.75,default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bonus that\Nyou get when I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.22,default,,0,0,0,,The stars are a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は別に用意する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.19,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のが１つ　あと２つは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.59,default,,0,0,0,,One of mine,\Nand the other two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.53,default,,0,0,0,,...from these two behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろ２人の星だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？あの それってまさか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.56,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.53,default,,0,0,0,,There is no other way left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう他に道はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな… 勘弁してくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.91,default,,0,0,0,,No way... Please let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.51,default,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.47,default,,0,0,0,,And duel to the death with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:58.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かって 俺と死んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何 言ってるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら残り時間が少ないからって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.69,default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.65,default,,0,0,0,,Just because there isn't time,\Nwe needn't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑　安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.04,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,We must take the leap now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 突っ走んなきゃダメなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り30分を切る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.60,default,,0,0,0,,Without six stars\Nbefore the last 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星６個くらいにしとかないと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話にならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.49,default,,0,0,0,,we won't have\Nany chance left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 神がかりを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作らなきゃダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:17.42,default,,0,0,0,,Unless we force a way out,\Nwe're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.78,default,,0,0,0,,No, no!\NI don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌っす 嫌っす　絶対に嫌っす
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが自分の星を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう賭けようと勝手っすけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.06,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, I don't care how\Nyou use your stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.97,default,,0,0,0,,But please don't drag us in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巻き込まないでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:29.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も撤回してください　撤回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.71,default,,0,0,0,,I don't agree to this either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ 撤回しくてださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いです カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.84,default,,0,0,0,,- Me too! Withdraw!\N- Just withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.51,default,,0,0,0,,- Take it back!\N- Withdraw, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:36.45,default,,0,0,0,,What fools. And to think\NI expected something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言い出すかと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらの言うとおりじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.15,default,,0,0,0,,But it's just as they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:45.08,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd let\Nsomeone else use your last star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の星 命を他人の判断で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けられちゃ たまらねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.12,default,,0,0,0,,They're a group of three formed\Nout of selfish reasons anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らもどうせ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,損得だけでくっついた３人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.83,default,,0,0,0,,The other two would\Ndefinitely not go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの２人は絶対 首を縦に振らない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負 成立しねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.54,default,,0,0,0,,This game can't be played.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.42,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お おう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.55,default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.51,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!\NKitami, you're running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！北見 逃げる気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.51,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. It's because\Nyou guys are wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい　お前らが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グダグダやってんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 まとめる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理無理　あばよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.89,default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.27,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible! Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.61,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:16.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:16.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分… せめて５分 時間をくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.32,default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes.\NGive me five minutes at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.30,default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くどいな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.32,default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.12,default,,0,0,0,,I already said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダだって言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まとめてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.29,default,,0,0,0,,- I'll settle it!\N- I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知るか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった　カネはやる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.75,default,,0,0,0,,I get it!\NI'll give you the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこの600万はやる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.53,default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the six million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分でまとまらなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この600万は持ってっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:35.40,default,,0,0,0,,If I can't get them to agree in\Nfive minutes, take this six million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.41,default,,0,0,0,,So, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.06,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何 言い出すんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.78,default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.28,default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 めちゃくちゃ言ってるんすか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 600万を失って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.28,default,,0,0,0,,What will we do if\Nwe lose that six million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目を覚ましてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボケども！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.52,default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目を覚ますのは てめえらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.07,default,,0,0,0,,You guys are the ones\Nwho should wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.32,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:06:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは今 絶望的に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:06:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切羽つまってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.73,default,,0,0,0,,Now, we're down\Nto our last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.99,default,,0,0,0,,There's only 46 minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと46分だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:05.83,default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have to\Nbet everything on luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運否天賦に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き死にをかけなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.77,default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボンクラ！このまま30分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,経ったとしたらどうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.23,default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if\N30 minutes pass at this rate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.70,default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be\Nany opponents left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対戦相手すらままならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.44,default,,0,0,0,,Going from three to nine stars\Nwould be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな状況で星３つから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９つなんて 夢のまた夢だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運否天賦すら成り立たねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし今ならその運否天賦で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.38,default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing\Nas luck by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:24.85,default,,0,0,0,,But now, we can at least\Nattempt to win by chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちが見える地点まで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは今 置かれてる状況が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:28.97,default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't understand\Nthe situation we're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:32.32,default,,0,0,0,,The flames are already\Nat our feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火の手はもう足を焼いてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめようかなんて発言は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.88,default,,0,0,0,,Quitting in this situation\Nwould be mere nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝言同然　前しかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.57,default,,0,0,0,,There is no way but forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.74,default,,0,0,0,,Running forward,\Nrunning forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突っ走って 突っ走って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その先にある亀裂を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,...with no way but to leap\Nover that chasm in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛び越えるしかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも まだ他にも道は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.57,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.84,default,,0,0,0,,But, there should be\Nsome other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.05,default,,0,0,0,,Understand your situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減 気づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,退路なんかもう ねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.25,default,,0,0,0,,There is nowhere left to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうまでして勝負に…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.81,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, why are you\Nso keen to duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.69,default,,0,0,0,,To win, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まってらあ　勝つためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.92,default,,0,0,0,,To get nine stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を９個にするためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残るためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.43,default,,0,0,0,,To survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:13.26,default,,0,0,0,,For all three of us to leave\Nthis ship with the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち３人が最後の最後に笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船を降りるためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.86,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.69,default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, have courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泣くな　勇気を出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.58,default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度３度なんて言わねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ１度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.68,default,,0,0,0,,Just once, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:27.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ１度だけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:31.15,default,,0,0,0,,Have courage, to survive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勇気を 生き残るための勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.32,default,,0,0,0,,He will never get them to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まとまるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ もうすぐ５分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.03,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.52,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, five minutes\Nwill soon be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.66,default,,0,0,0,,We'll accept their\Nlast remaining profits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もらってやらあ この残りカスを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説得したぞ 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.27,default,,0,0,0,,I've convinced them, Kitami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.24,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？お前らいいのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.71,default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys fine with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　勝負します
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もやります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.56,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.18,default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.20,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami, the deal\Nfor three stars is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見 勝負だ　星３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え… いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.53,default,,0,0,0,,No, at such short notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:09.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな急に言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってんだ てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.05,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.04,default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:19.32,default,,0,0,0,,You were ready to\Ntake the cash, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 今 カネを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていこうとしたじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.45,default,,0,0,0,,It'd have been yours only\Nif this game was cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負がまとまらなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていくつもりだった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.27,default,,0,0,0,,But when it's settled,\Nhow could you withdraw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに いざとなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降りるなんてあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.67,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose,\Nyou won't go to the other room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに てめえらは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に負けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.87,default,,0,0,0,,You still have a safety net!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室に落ちるわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セーフティだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆病もいい加減にしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.71,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.96,default,,0,0,0,,With a sum of six million\Nupon winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大体 こっちが600万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上乗せしてる分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.15,default,,0,0,0,,you have more to gain than us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った時の利は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らのほうが大きい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:42.41,default,,0,0,0,,But you keep looking back without\Neven trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに つかもうとしないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救いようもなく後向き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.21,default,,0,0,0,,Those who look forward\Nstill have opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前向きのバカなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ可能性はあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.86,default,,0,0,0,,but those who look back,\Nhave none.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後向きならゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い切ってやらあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.42,default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.39,default,,0,0,0,,You will never have\N100% success!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には100パーセント
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,成功などない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のことさ　臆病 臆病！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.05,default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:58.50,default,,0,0,0,,You'll simply chicken out\Nuntil your brain degrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆病ばっかで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳まで退化してやがんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの生きてるなんて言わねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ心臓や肺が動いてるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.80,default,,0,0,0,,That's not called living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.34,default,,0,0,0,,It's simply functioning\Nby your heart and lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダだから さっさと死ねや
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いこと言わねえから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.59,default,,0,0,0,,You're a waste of space,\Nso die off quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.97,default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't blame you\Nif you consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世間の迷惑を考えて 今すぐ死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船 降りたらすぐによ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:09.54,default,,0,0,0,,...dying now and\Nsparing the world of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.73,default,,0,0,0,,Die, as soon as\Nyou get off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前な…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ　何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.51,default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.13,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.06,default,,0,0,0,,Are you getting mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しはカリカリきたんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒れ 怒れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.41,default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and fume!\NThat's only normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ正常だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてるってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.72,default,,0,0,0,,It's proof that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.69,default,,0,0,0,,Think hard,\Nnow that you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来たら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.53,default,,0,0,0,,You have to play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見さん やっちゃいましょうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.85,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami, just give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな奴にツキなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう残っちゃいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.79,default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that loud-mouth\Nstay around anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もそう思います
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.45,default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.87,default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him off after\Ninsulting us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうまで言われて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙ってることないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.49,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,Let's play, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるか カイジ　受けてやらあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.95,default,,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構 結構　臆病野郎も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.26,default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:02.43,default,,0,0,0,,It shows that a chicken like you\Nstill has some guts left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,根性まではビビりくさって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかったってわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:07.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジと北見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:07.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つのギャンブル ついに成立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:07.38,default,,0,0,0,,The gamble between Kitami and\NKaiji for three stars is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.52,default,,0,0,0,,Time is drawing close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時 満ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人 向き合う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.78,default,,0,0,0,,They face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に動き出したのはカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.75,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji makes the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グー チョキ パーの中から
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚を選択
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.34,default,,0,0,0,,He chooses one of\Nthe Rock, Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.90,default,,0,0,0,,...and Paper cards in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.30,default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that,\NKitami also makes his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを見て北見も動く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき胸ポケットにしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚のカードを取り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:37.39,default,,0,0,0,,He took out the card he'd put\Ninto his breast pocket just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを待っていたかのように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,背後から人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.87,default,,0,0,0,,And as if waiting for that,\Npeople appeared behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.52,default,,0,0,0,,They were surrounded\Nto be brought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたら即 別室に連行するため
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.69,default,,0,0,0,,...to the other room\Nimmediately upon losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:52.58,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね 死ねばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.68,default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.53,default,,0,0,0,,You should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.55,default,,0,0,0,,Lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けろ　負けろ　負けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:01.52,default,,0,0,0,,Lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.00,default,,0,0,0,,Please, lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その声は気のせいではない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに聞こえるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.52,default,,0,0,0,,The voices weren't\Nfrom Kaiji's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.99,default,,0,0,0,,They were audible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:13.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:13.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底に誘う亡者の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:13.50,default,,0,0,0,,The voices of the lost\Ncalling them to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ こいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.23,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.20,default,,0,0,0,,What's up with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気にするな　ゴミどもだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.33,default,,0,0,0,,Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:19.96,default,,0,0,0,,They're just trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.21,default,,0,0,0,,The voices belonged to those\Nwithout enough stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声の主は 星いたらない者たち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:29.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちが負ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:29.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その分 フロア内の人が減り
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:29.18,default,,0,0,0,,If Kaiji loses, there would\Nbe fewer people on that floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の入手が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらかとは言え容易になる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.55,default,,0,0,0,,Hence, it would be easier\Nfor them to get the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らの望むはカイジたちの失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破綻　破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.88,default,,0,0,0,,All of them\Nwished for Kaiji to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.35,default,,0,0,0,,To fail, and be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャラリーはこっちの味方だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.22,default,,0,0,0,,The gallery is on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:50.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな気分だ？四面楚歌の中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:50.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の星を賭けるっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.89,default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.99,default,,0,0,0,,To be surrounded by enemies\Nand betting on your last star?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.27,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.32,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人なんか関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.47,default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing\Nto do with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.77,default,,0,0,0,,It involves me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だ　俺なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.24,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肝心なのは いつも どんな時も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:03.49,default,,0,0,0,,What matters is to decide\Nfor myself at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がやると決めてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただそれだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.12,default,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついたんだ　耳を傾けるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人のごたくじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:11.45,default,,0,0,0,,I realised not to listen to\Nothers', but to my own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺自身の声　信じるべきは俺の力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.32,default,,0,0,0,,And to have faith\Nin my own abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢沸騰点｣　水が水蒸気に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.86,default,,0,0,0,,Boiling point is when\Nwater turns to steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:24.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな変わり目をカイジは今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:24.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身の内に感じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:23.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji could now feel it\Nwithin his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己が存在のリアリティ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり｢生｣を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.35,default,,0,0,0,,His own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.04,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.74,default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of being alive\Nat this very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 確かに生きているという感触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その震えを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.71,default,,0,0,0,,...trembles within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.71,default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:38.94,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:45.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.72,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けが込んでいる こいつに今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち運があるものか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.89,default,,0,0,0,,He's going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.69,default,,0,0,0,,He has no winning streak now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.06,default,,0,0,0,,The flow of the game\Nis with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:54.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れは俺　俺はこの最後の戦いに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:54.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ってあがる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:53.76,default,,0,0,0,,I will win this last match\Nand rise up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この余分なカードを使い切って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.26,default,,0,0,0,,...by using up\Nthis extra card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待った！この勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,審判！セットに入ったんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.50,default,,0,0,0,,Stop the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.70,default,,0,0,0,,Referee, the game is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時点での中断なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認めるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.67,default,,0,0,0,,Is withdrawal\Nallowed at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認められない　セットに入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中断は一切 認められない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.18,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:13.88,default,,0,0,0,,Once you have "Set",\Nno withdrawal is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな いいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.90,default,,0,0,0,,No way! Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:21.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に勝負をしないって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:21.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わけじゃない　ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if we're ending\Nthe game, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードのチェンジも認めない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.86,default,,0,0,0,,No changing of cards\Nis allowed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セットに入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはただ開くだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.49,default,,0,0,0,,Once you have "Set",\Nyou can only open the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:32.76,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami, you heard him!\NPut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見 聞いてのとおりだ　置け！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを置け　置け！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.60,default,,0,0,0,,Put the card down!\NPut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.23,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:48.65,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but right now\NI have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:49.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からねえ　分からねえが今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:49.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な予感が走った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:54.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か決定的な欠陥 ほつれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:53.35,default,,0,0,0,,Somehow,\Nthere's a fatal flaw in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてがバラバラに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほどけ散り 崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.13,default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that\Neverything will unravel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.14,default,,0,0,0,,...and come crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな予感が…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい勘してるぜ 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.00,default,,0,0,0,,Your intuition is sharp, Kitami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりさ　ほつれはあった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決定的なほつれがな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.66,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, there is a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.80,default,,0,0,0,,A fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.00,default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Kitami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えてるか 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が俺たちの前に姿を現し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:20.77,default,,0,0,0,,What you said when you\Nfirst appeared before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負を申し込んだ時に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番最初に口にした言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.01,default,,0,0,0,,and challenged me to a duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:26.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前との戦いが最後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.06,default,,0,0,0,,This match with you\Nis our last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:30.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは勝っても負けても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:30.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２階へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:29.08,default,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, we're rising up\Nto the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この発言がとんだミス
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが ほつれのその１
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.29,default,,0,0,0,,That statement\Nwas a grave mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.26,default,,0,0,0,,That was your first flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２つめのほつれは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざ勝負をしようとした時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.73,default,,0,0,0,,The second was that\Nwhen you were ready to duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が何のちゅうちょもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚のカードを手にしたことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:43.70,default,,0,0,0,,you picked a card\Nwithout hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に使う１枚を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.62,default,,0,0,0,,The decision for which card\Nto use at the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の判断だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決められるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.16,default,,0,0,0,,...could not have been\Nyour decision alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それができるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に出すカードについて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:56.34,default,,0,0,0,,So, there was an agreement\Non which card to use last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合意がなされてたってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これに さっきのほつれを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つなぎ合わせると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.84,default,,0,0,0,,Putting this together\Nwith your other mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おのずと ある理が浮かび上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.99,default,,0,0,0,,your way of reasoning\Ncan be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:06.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりお前らがこの最終戦で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:06.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出すであろうカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.42,default,,0,0,0,,Also, it shows which card\Nyou will use in this last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.68,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には分かるのさ　俺とお前は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.49,default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.87,default,,0,0,0,,We are birds of\Nthe same feather,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:17.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占めなんて戦略を考え出した
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:17.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ穴のムジナ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.96,default,,0,0,0,,who thought of\Nthe same strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にはお前の余分なカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:21.38,default,,0,0,0,,That's how I know\Nwhat your extra card is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして なぜこの男に分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:26.67,default,,0,0,0,,No way! How?!\NHow does this guy know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.64,default,,0,0,0,,...that this is an extra card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカードが余分なんてことが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.42,default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.35,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:35.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジさん 余分って一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.49,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 北見にはどうしても消したい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔なカードができちまったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:39.48,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Kitami also has a card\Nwhich he wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.35,default,,0,0,0,,...get rid of,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単さ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.76,default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間うちで あいこ照合するには
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.88,default,,0,0,0,,By using draws\Nto get rid of their cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手元のカードがすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶数でないとダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.10,default,,0,0,0,,the Rock, Scissors and Paper\Ncards must be in even numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.47,default,,0,0,0,,If not, the stars will\Nmove among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでないと勝負の後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間うちで星が動いちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:16:01.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見たちは当然 手元のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:16:01.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶数でそろえようとしたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.61,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami and gang would\Ndefinitely try to maintain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.44,default,,0,0,0,,...an even number of\Ncards in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに１枚 余分なカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できたってわけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:04.64,default,,0,0,0,,But one extra card was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初の｢この戦いが最後だ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:08.23,default,,0,0,0,,When he said that this\Nwould be the last game,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢１回だけ戦いたい｣ってことで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:13.50,default,,0,0,0,,it meant he only wanted one\Nmatch to get rid of that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消したいカードがあるってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに さっきの合意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.49,default,,0,0,0,,And the agreement\Nthat they have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使う１枚のカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まってたってのがその裏づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:20.22,default,,0,0,0,,...also means that as long\Nthe extra card is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:25.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり余分な１枚がなくなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:25.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りはすべて偶数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:25.22,default,,0,0,0,,there would be an even number\Nof cards remaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこで残りのカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて消せる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.23,default,,0,0,0,,They can then get rid of\Nall the cards by drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろ 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.26,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kitami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.20,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.26,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, something\Ndoesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 何か雲行きが怪しいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの北見って奴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追い詰められてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:39.38,default,,0,0,0,,That Kitami seems to\Nhave been cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！問題は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が余分なカードかってことだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.93,default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.29,default,,0,0,0,,The real question here\Nis what the extra card is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが言い当てられなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなお題目も絵に描いた餅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.83,default,,0,0,0,,Unless you get that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.47,default,,0,0,0,,whatever you said\Nis for bedtime stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.59,default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't mean a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソの役にも立ちゃしねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見 明白なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.86,default,,0,0,0,,Kitami, it's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな バカを言うな　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.95,default,,0,0,0,,Rubbish...\NDon't talk rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.86,default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん絶対とは言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.55,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have no guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理に合わぬことが起きれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでだ　しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.05,default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work according\Nto logic, then too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:07.91,default,,0,0,0,,But if I reason it\Nin the usual way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常どおりの流れで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事が推移したと考えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のどのカードが余分かは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:11.43,default,,0,0,0,,what your extra card is\Nwould be crystal clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.34,default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い占めカードではないグーと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキが偶数になった時点で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.45,default,,0,0,0,,You probably stopped buying\Nwhen the Rocks and Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買うのをやめたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.00,default,,0,0,0,,...you didn't need,\Ntotalled to even numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:25.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこの２つが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:25.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶数である可能性はかなり高い
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.10,default,,0,0,0,,So, it's highly possible\Nthat you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.85,default,,0,0,0,,...an even number\Nof these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてパーだ　お前らは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーで勝負に走る俺たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.31,default,,0,0,0,,Next, is Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.92,default,,0,0,0,,You challenged us,\Nwho bought Rocks cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーてやる気でいた　とすると
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.10,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何回パーで勝負するかは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.96,default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how many times\Nyou'd have to use Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら無理に偶数に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろえる意味はない　違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.14,default,,0,0,0,,So there is no need to\Nmake its number even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.57,default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 今 奇数
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:47.88,default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, your extra card\Nwould be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:49.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち 余ってるカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.51,default,,0,0,0,,Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.68,default,,0,0,0,,Open it, Kitami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開けろ 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.28,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るは貴様のカードだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開けろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.65,default,,0,0,0,,What's left is just your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:00.86,default,,0,0,0,,Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃー！勝った！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりましたね カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.72,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.79,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ 星３つですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.50,default,,0,0,0,,You survived, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:40.07,default,,0,0,0,,After being driven to\Nonly three stars left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 生き残る！残り40分で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つに追い詰められたが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでまた星３つを奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.16,default,,0,0,0,,...in the last 40 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.36,default,,0,0,0,,he won three more stars back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び 希望の灯ともる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.83,default,,0,0,0,,Once again, there is a\Nray of hope for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.89,default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人てのが生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.02,default,,0,0,0,,We survived because\Nthere are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 覚えてるか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーの買い占めに走ってる時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:58.22,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, do you remember\Nwhat you asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレで俺にこう言ったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.42,default,,0,0,0,,...after we bought the cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ２枚 パー４枚ってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し 心もとなくないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:03.38,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it unsafe to have\Njust four Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.15,default,,0,0,0,,...and two Paper cards\Nin our deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い足しておいたほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.05,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should buy more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.47,default,,0,0,0,,That saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:14.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:14.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢目立つ動きはやめよう｣と言って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.29,default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop buying,\Nin order not to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買い足すのをやめたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは建て前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:18.10,default,,0,0,0,,...raise suspicion, but that\Nwasn't the real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:22.68,default,,0,0,0,,The real reason is\Nthe draws after we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った後の あいこ照合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ２ パー４という
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶数の状況は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.35,default,,0,0,0,,With two Scissors\Nand four Papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこで照合するには好都合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.47,default,,0,0,0,,it is ideal to draw\Nas the numbers are even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから買い足しは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必要ないと決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.00,default,,0,0,0,,That's why there was\Nno need to buy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この１件があったから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北見の最終戦の申し出に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:38.45,default,,0,0,0,,I was reminded of this when Kitami\Nchallenged me to a last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:42.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピーンときて 奴には奇数の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:42.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードが１種あるんじゃないかと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:43.53,default,,0,0,0,,It led me to predict that\Nhe might have an odd card left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう ひらめいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.86,default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いがけず 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役に立ってたんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.42,default,,0,0,0,,I was useful even\Nwithout knowing it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ　こういうことが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グループの力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.09,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:51.02,default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人じゃ素通りしちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発想や定石を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:56.10,default,,0,0,0,,Your team mates can point out\Nthe things you don't realise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:58.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間が確認させてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:58.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑と安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:20:00.31,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Ando, it's because\Nof you guys that we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前ら２人がいたから勝てたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.32,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい待て 北見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 これは一体どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.81,default,,0,0,0,,Hey Kitami, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.24,default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らのせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.48,default,,0,0,0,,You guys are to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが急がせなけりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は気づいていたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.58,default,,0,0,0,,If you guys hadn't pressured me,\NI'd have predicted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちのせいだって言うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.47,default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying\Nthis was our fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　今回の敗因はお前らだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.66,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's your fault\Nthat we lost this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.15,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってやがる　そもそも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦なんて口を滑らせたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:24.73,default,,0,0,0,,You let slip that\Nit's our last game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.43,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ろくすっぽ 頭も回らねえくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガタガタ言ってんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:29.17,default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk so much when your\Nbrains aren't even working!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:33.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？元々 原因は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:33.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえの独断だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.37,default,,0,0,0,,What? We lost because\Nyou were too impulsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:33.67,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑　安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.57,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.24,default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢毒を食わらば皿までも｣か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.65,default,,0,0,0,,Let us aim\Nfor the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.80,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:51.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢毒皿｣でいくか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:51.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味ですか それ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.61,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.22,default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーも買い占めだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.16,default,,0,0,0,,Let's buy up Paper too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちに足りない星は３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.76,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and gang still need\Nthree more stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとのない状況は変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り時間は40分を切る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:09.80,default,,0,0,0,,Their desperate situation\Nremains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.16,default,,0,0,0,,The time remaining\Nis 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.14,default,,0,0,0,,They must move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へ行かなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.24,default,,0,0,0,,Much further forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.63,default,,0,0,0,,Forward, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へ 前へ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　｢興亡｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.84,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Rise and Fall.
